text:
1. I think that they have to make at least one commit to the project to be publicly viewed as a contributor. 
2. I mentioned in the announcement I just posted that we are hoping to get through everyone's by Monday. Check there fore more dates-related info if your group doesn't pass.
3. Github Projects is listed as the required project management tool in the Project Guidelines doc in Pages on Canvas. If you are using another tool, you can link it in a card on Github Projects.
